OL,3,CCouncil insists special educational
OL,4,Cneeds services for pupils are improving
OL,6,FThe council said it has more than a
OL,7,F100 different targets, and are almost
OL,8,Fhalf way towards achieving them.
OL,10,FChallenging Cllr Love on what actual
OL,11,F'nuts and bolts' improvements have
OL,12,Fbeen made for pupils, he said: "We're
OL,13,Fworking with our partners, with the
OL,14,FNHS, with the educational
OL,15,Festablishments right across Kent to
OL,16,Fmake improvements to the whole of the
OL,17,Fsystem.
OL,19,F"The backlog in speech and language
OL,20,Fassessments has fallen from over 500
OL,21,Fto just over 100 now.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
