OL,3,CCouncil insists special educational
OL,4,Cneeds services for pupils are improving
OL,6,F"We're setting up new models of local
OL,7,Fschools working together in area
OL,8,Fgroups, in locality groups, so that
OL,9,Fthey can share some good practice.
OL,11,F"And there's still more work to do and
OL,12,FI want to make the point that, you
OL,13,Fknow, we are, this is work in
OL,14,Fprogress, we are continuing with the
OL,15,Ftask.
OL,17,F"We're speeding up timescales for
OL,18,Fprocessing, and looking to improve the
OL,19,Fplacements. We know we're not there
OL,20,Fyet. We're not complacent about it.
