OL,6,F"We know we've got more to do."
OL,8,FLast year, (KCC) was , and the
OL,9,Fgovernment threatened to take away
OL,10,Fcontrol of services away from the
OL,11,Fauthority.
OL,13,FOne year on from this, families say
OL,14,Fthings have only deteriorated further,
OL,15,Fdespite Kent County Council's claims
OL,16,Fthat things have improved.
