OL,3,CCouncil insists special educational
OL,4,Cneeds services for pupils are improving
OL,6,F"We're in touch with families all the
OL,7,Ftime and we get that sort of feedback,
OL,8,Fbut we also get feedback that says
OL,9,Fthat things are really going well,"
OL,10,FClllr Love added.
OL,12,F"It is a mixed picture at the moment,
OL,13,Fbut I think looking objectively at the
OL,14,Fstatistics, it shows that we're
OL,15,Factually working in the right
OL,16,Fdirection."
