OL,6,FLots of families have told ITV
OL,7,FMeridian they feel their children are
OL,8,Fbeing inappropriately placed into
OL,9,Fmainstream schools which aren't always
OL,10,Fable to provide the appropriate
OL,11,Fsupport.
OL,13,FBut Cllr Rory Love maintains that
OL,14,Fmainstream schools are better for
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,17,F"They give better outcomes," he added.
